data.description: The home you've been waiting for... Step on in to this beautifully updated 4 bedroom ranch that is just beaming with tons natural light! It is conveniently located just down the street to Armstrong and Memorial Park, Jay Stream Middle School, Carol Stream Library and more. All finishes have been recently updated in kitchen boasting Butcher Block countertops and Frigidaire Gallery SS appliances! New Luxury Plank Waterproof Laminate flooring throughout entire main level. Conveniently off the bedrooms is the laundry room, fitted with Front load Kenmore Dryer and Amana Washer (2023). Custom Faux Wood Cordless blinds in all bedrooms. Enjoy entertaining all summer long on your Maintenance free TREX deck! This home won't last long!
